      <title>理想汽车推出世界上最大的电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/li-auto-unveils-what-it-says-is-world-s-biggest-electric-car</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于北京的理想汽车公司在推迟几个月后于周五推出了首款纯电动汽车，以寻求在中国获得优势——世界上最拥挤、竞争最激烈的汽车市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/li-auto-unveils-what-it-says-is-world-s-biggest-electric-car</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 09:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
