      <title>人工智能前景令人兴奋，戴尔股价飙升至创纪录水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/dell-reports-sales-that-top-estimates-on-ai-server-excitement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受处理人工智能工作的信息技术设备需求的推动，戴尔科技公司 (Dell Technologies Inc.) 的销售额和利润好于预期，股价飙升 38%，创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/dell-reports-sales-that-top-estimates-on-ai-server-excitement</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 21:12:26 GMT</pubDate>
